      *              * Uscita                                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     tdo-ric-sel-999.
       tdo-ric-sel-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Trattamento errore                              *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Visualizzazione messaggio                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   box-msg-err-000      thru box-msg-err-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Uscita con errore                           *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "#"                  to   w-cnt-tdo-ric-flg      .
       tdo-ric-sel-999.
           exit.

